		"description": "<p>At 5th level, you gain the ability to manipulate the strands of fortune and fate. You may do so a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, regaining expended uses on a long rest. Choose one of the following:</p><h3>Witch&rsquo;s Blessing</h3><p>When a creature you can see fails an ability check, attack roll, or saving throw, you may use your reaction to apply a bonus equal to 1d4 + your spellcasting ability modifier, potentially changing the result of the roll.</p><h3>Witch&rsquo;s Curse</h3><p>When a creature you can see succeeds on an ability check, attack roll, or saving throws, you may use your reaction to apply a penalty equal to 1d4 + your spellcasting ability modifier.</p>",
